ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Ontario Fishery Regulations, 1989 and the Ontario Fishery Regulations, 2007
PrecisRegulations Amending the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1989 AND THE ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 2007, in order to (1) correct typographical or grammatical errors; (2) correct discrepancies between the French and English versions; (3)improve consistency in terminology; (4) update terminology; (5) add clarity to a regulatory provision; and, (6) other miscellaneous changes; update the name of a provincial ministry; to resolve discrepancies in names and coordinates, etc.
